    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "arnica cream sounds easy enough. do u think i can just use a bunch of it to speed things up? like if i put it on like every hour it'll definitely take the swelling down? and if i take some ibuprofen with it should be fine to just stay home and rest it for the weekend?",
